(125, 'Index Finger Workout', 'Index Finger Workout', '', 13, 1, 'LESSON', 1, '<img src=\"/uploads/finger_workout.png\" align=\"right\" /><p class=\"typinghelp\" /><br /><br /><br /><br />Таны хуруунууд дасгалтай уулзах цаг боллоо! Бид таны долоовор хурууг ажиллуулж эхлүүлэх гэж байна (эрхий хурууны дараах эхний хуруу). Хурууныхаа булчинг зохих ёсоор ажиллуулахын тулд энэ хичээлийг олон удаа хийхийг танд зөвлөж байна.<br /></p>', '<img src=\"/uploads/finger_workout.png\" align=\"right\" /><p class=\"typinghelp\" /><br /><br /><br /><br />It\\\'s time for your fingers to hit the gym!  We\\\'re going to start you out by working out your index finger (the first finger after your thumb).  I recommend you do this lesson multiple times to really work your finger\\\'s muscles.<br /></p>', 0, '<p class=\\\"typinghelp\\\">That was a short preview of this premium lesson. The full lesson is much longer and more comprehensive.<\\/p>  <p class=\\\"typinghelp\\\"><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.bicheech.com\\/upgrade\\/membership\\/\\\">Upgrading to a Gold Membership<\\/a> will remove all advertisements, unlock all premium content, and allow for priority email support.<\\/p><br \\/><p style=\\\"text-align:center\\\" class=\\\"typinghelp\\\"><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.bicheech.com\\/upgrade\\/membership\\/\\\" target=\\\"_top\\\">UPGRADE ACCOUNT<\\/a><\\/p>', '<p class=\\\"typinghelp\\\">That was a short preview of this premium lesson. The full lesson is much longer and more comprehensive.<\\/p>  <p class=\\\"typinghelp\\\"><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.bicheech.com\\/upgrade\\/membership\\/\\\">Upgrading to a Gold Membership<\\/a> will remove all advertisements, unlock all premium content, and allow for priority email support.<\\/p><br \\/><p style=\\\"text-align:center\\\" class=\\\"typinghelp\\\"><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.bicheech.com\\/upgrade\\/membership\\/\\\" target=\\\"_top\\\">UPGRADE ACCOUNT<\\/a><\\/p>', 'keyboard', 8),
(126, 'Ring Finger Workout', 'Ring Finger Workout', '', 14, 1, 'LESSON', 1, '<img src=\"/uploads/finger_workout.png\" align=\"right\" /><p class=\"typinghelp\" /><br /><br /><br /><br />Wow, your fingers are looking pretty ripped.  Again, we will be working the familiar workout routine, but this time with the ring finger, found 3 fingers over from the thumb.  Good luck!<br /></p>', '<img src=\"/uploads/finger_workout.png\" align=\"right\" /><p class=\"typinghelp\" /><br /><br /><br /><br />Wow, your fingers are looking pretty ripped.  Again, we will be working the familiar workout routine, but this time with the ring finger, found 3 fingers over from the thumb.  Good luck!<br /></p>', 0, '<p class=\\\"typinghelp\\\">That was a short preview of this premium lesson. The full lesson is much longer and more comprehensive.<\\/p>  <p class=\\\"typinghelp\\\"><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.bicheech.com\\/upgrade\\/membership\\/\\\">Upgrading to a Gold Membership<\\/a> will remove all advertisements, unlock all premium content, and allow for priority email support.<\\/p><br \\/><p style=\\\"text-align:center\\\" class=\\\"typinghelp\\\"><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.bicheech.com\\/upgrade\\/membership\\/\\\" target=\\\"_top\\\">UPGRADE ACCOUNT<\\/a><\\/p>', '<p class=\\\"typinghelp\\\">That was a short preview of this premium lesson. The full lesson is much longer and more comprehensive.<\\/p>  <p class=\\\"typinghelp\\\"><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.bicheech.com\\/upgrade\\/membership\\/\\\">Upgrading to a Gold Membership<\\/a> will remove all advertisements, unlock all premium content, and allow for priority email support.<\\/p><br \\/><p style=\\\"text-align:center\\\" class=\\\"typinghelp\\\"><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.bicheech.com\\/upgrade\\/membership\\/\\\" target=\\\"_top\\\">UPGRADE ACCOUNT<\\/a><\\/p>', 'keyboard', 9),
(127, 'Middle Finger Workout', 'Middle Finger Workout', '', 15, 1, 'LESSON', 1, '<img src=\"/uploads/finger_workout.png\" align=\"right\" /><p class=\"typinghelp\" /><br /><br /><br /><br />За, Одоо таны долоовор хуруу тод цохиж байгаа тул бид дунд хуруу руу шилжин орж байна (эрхий хуруунаас хоёр дахь хуруу). Энэ хичээл нь хурууныхаа булчинг бэхжүүлэх, хуруугаа байрлуулахад дасгал хийхэд туслах ерөнхий дасгалуудыг багтаасан болно.<br /></p>', '<img src=\"/uploads/finger_workout.png\" align=\"right\" /><p class=\"typinghelp\" /><br /><br /><br /><br />Alrighty, now that your index finger is nice and buff, we\\\'re going to move into the middle finger (the second finger over from your thumb).  This lesson features the same general drills to help strengthen your finger\\\'s muscles as well as drill you on finger placement.<br /></p>', 0, '<p class=\\\"typinghelp\\\">That was a short preview of this premium lesson. The full lesson is much longer and more comprehensive.<\\/p>  <p class=\\\"typinghelp\\\"><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.bicheech.com\\/upgrade\\/membership\\/\\\">Upgrading to a Gold Membership<\\/a> will remove all advertisements, unlock all premium content, and allow for priority email support.<\\/p><br \\/><p style=\\\"text-align:center\\\" class=\\\"typinghelp\\\"><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.bicheech.com\\/upgrade\\/membership\\/\\\" target=\\\"_top\\\">UPGRADE ACCOUNT<\\/a><\\/p>', '<p class=\\\"typinghelp\\\">That was a short preview of this premium lesson. The full lesson is much longer and more comprehensive.<\\/p>  <p class=\\\"typinghelp\\\"><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.bicheech.com\\/upgrade\\/membership\\/\\\">Upgrading to a Gold Membership<\\/a> will remove all advertisements, unlock all premium content, and allow for priority email support.<\\/p><br \\/><p style=\\\"text-align:center\\\" class=\\\"typinghelp\\\"><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.bicheech.com\\/upgrade\\/membership\\/\\\" target=\\\"_top\\\">UPGRADE ACCOUNT<\\/a><\\/p>', 'keyboard', 8),
(128, 'Pinky Finger Workout', 'Pinky Finger Workout', '', 16, 1, 'LESSON', 1, '<img src=\"/uploads/finger_workout.png\" align=\"right\" /><p class=\"typinghelp\" /><br /><br /><br /><br />Wow you\\\'re doing great!  You\\\'ve managed to move all the way down the line to the pinky finger!  This is the last finger on your hand and will be the most difficult to get used to using properly.  I recommend you type this lesson many times!<br /></p>', '<img src=\"/uploads/finger_workout.png\" align=\"right\" /><p class=\"typinghelp\" /><br /><br /><br /><br />Wow you\\\'re doing great!  You\\\'ve managed to move all the way down the line to the pinky finger!  This is the last finger on your hand and will be the most difficult to get used to using properly.  I recommend you type this lesson many times!<br /></p>', 0, '<p class=\\\"typinghelp\\\">That was a short preview of this premium lesson. The full lesson is much longer and more comprehensive.<\\/p>  <p class=\\\"typinghelp\\\"><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.bicheech.com\\/upgrade\\/membership\\/\\\">Upgrading to a Gold Membership<\\/a> will remove all advertisements, unlock all premium content, and allow for priority email support.<\\/p><br \\/><p style=\\\"text-align:center\\\" class=\\\"typinghelp\\\"><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.bicheech.com\\/upgrade\\/membership\\/\\\" target=\\\"_top\\\">UPGRADE ACCOUNT<\\/a><\\/p>', '<p class=\\\"typinghelp\\\">That was a short preview of this premium lesson. The full lesson is much longer and more comprehensive.<\\/p>  <p class=\\\"typinghelp\\\"><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.bicheech.com\\/upgrade\\/membership\\/\\\">Upgrading to a Gold Membership<\\/a> will remove all advertisements, unlock all premium content, and allow for priority email support.<\\/p><br \\/><p style=\\\"text-align:center\\\" class=\\\"typinghelp\\\"><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.bicheech.com\\/upgrade\\/membership\\/\\\" target=\\\"_top\\\">UPGRADE ACCOUNT<\\/a><\\/p>', 'keyboard', 9),
(316, 'Нүүр Мөрны Товчнууд', 'The Home Row Keys', 'HOME_ROW', 1, 0, 'LESSON', 1, '<p class=\"typinghelp\">Бид \"Үндсэн Мөр\" дээр эхэлж <strong>долоовор хуруугаараа <key>F</key> ба <key>J</key> товчнуудыг сурч эхэлнэ</strong>.<p><p class=\"typinghelp\">Зөвлөмж: Таны гар дээрх эдгээр товчлуурууд нь <strong>өргөгдсөн товгор</strong> байгааг анзаараарай. Эдгээр товгор-ууд нь таны гар руу доош харуулахгүйгээр, үндсэн мөрийг <strong>гараараа мэдэрч хайх боломжийг олгоно</strong>.</p><br /><center><img src=\"/typing/images/intros/f_j.png\" alt=\"Home row Finger Position\" /></center>', '<p class=\"typinghelp\">We are going to begin on the \"Home Row\", <strong>learning the <key>F</key> and <key>J</key> keys</strong> with your index fingers. <p><p class=\"typinghelp\">Tip: Notice the <strong>raised bumps</strong> on these keys on your keyboard. These bumps allow you to <strong>find the home row by touch</strong>, without looking down at your keyboard.</p><br /><center><img src=\"/typing/images/intros/f_j.png\" alt=\"Home row Finger Position\" /></center>', 1, '<img src=\\\"\\/tutor\\/images\\/congrats_1.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" align=\\\"left\\\" style=\\\"padding: 20px\\\" \\/><p class=\\\"typinghelp\\\">You have just completed the first Bicheech.com lesson!   How does it feel to know your Home Row keys?<\\/p><p class=\\\"typinghelp\\\">Depending on your comfort level with the Home Row you may want to repeat this lesson, however it is suggested that you move on to the Top and Bottom rows.  You will be reviewing the Home Row keys in future lessons.<\\/p><p class=\\\"typinghelp\\\">You\'re doing great, so keep it up!<\\/p>', '<img src=\\\"\\/tutor\\/images\\/congrats_1.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" align=\\\"left\\\" style=\\\"padding: 20px\\\" \\/><p class=\\\"typinghelp\\\">You have just completed the first Bicheech.com lesson!   How does it feel to know your Home Row keys?<\\/p><p class=\\\"typinghelp\\\">Depending on your comfort level with the Home Row you may want to repeat this lesson, however it is suggested that you move on to the Top and Bottom rows.  You will be reviewing the Home Row keys in future lessons.<\\/p><p class=\\\"typinghelp\\\">You\'re doing great, so keep it up!<\\/p>', 'Keyboard', 1),
(317, 'Дээд Мөрны Товчнууд', 'The Top Row Keys', 'TOP_ROW', 2, 0, 'LESSON', 1, '<p class=\"typinghelp\">Бид одоо Дээд Мөр гэж нэрлэдэг, Үндсэн Мөрийн яг дээрх товчнууд шилжиж байна. Бид <strong><key>R</key> болон <key>U</key> товч</strong>лууруудаас эхэлж долоовор хуруугаараа бичиж эхэлнэ.</p><p class=\"typinghelp\"><strong>Үндсэн мөр дээр хуруугаа байлгаж байхаа санаж байгаарай</strong>, зөвхөн нэг хуруугаа нэг л хөдөлгөнө.</p><br /><center><img src=\"/typing/images/intros/r_u.png\" alt=\"Дээд эгнээний хурууны байршил\" /></center>', '<p class=\"typinghelp\">We are now going to move into the keys just above the Home Row, known as the Top Row.  We will begin with <strong>the <key>R</key> and <key>U</key> keys</strong> which you will type with your index fingers.</p><p class=\"typinghelp\">Remember to always <strong>keep your fingers resting on the Home Row</strong>, and only move one finger at a time.</p><br /><center><img src=\"/typing/images/intros/r_u.png\" alt=\"Home row Finger Position\" /></center>', 1, '<img src=\\\"\\/tutor\\/images\\/congrats_2.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" align=\\\"left\\\" style=\\\"padding-right: 20px\\\" \\/><p class=\\\"typinghelp\\\">You are now a Top Row genius!  It was just that simple.  Off you go to the Bottom Row.  I saved that one for last because, well, it is a tad harder... just a smidgen though, so relax.<\\/p>', '<img src=\\\"\\/tutor\\/images\\/congrats_2.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" align=\\\"left\\\" style=\\\"padding-right: 20px\\\" \\/><p class=\\\"typinghelp\\\">You are now a Top Row genius!  It was just that simple.  Off you go to the Bottom Row.  I saved that one for last because, well, it is a tad harder... just a smidgen though, so relax.<\\/p>', 'Keyboard', 1);
