(371, 'Dvorak Keyboard', 'Dvorak Keyboard', '', 7, 0, 'LESSON', 1, '<p class=\\\"typinghelp\\\">This lesson is to teach you the Dvorak system of typing.  It is known to allow faster typing because the keys are placed strategically to allow faster finger movement.  QWERTY, on the other hand, was invented to slow a typist down so typewriters would not jam.<\\/p><p class=\\\"typinghelp\\\">This is actually quite a long lesson, and covers all there is to learn of Dvorak, so I hope you get something out of it.<\\/p><p class=\\\"typinghelp\\\"><strong>Be sure to click the \\\"Language & Keyboard\\\" link above and switch to the Dvorak layout if you want to see the proper on-screen keyboard.  Note: You can type this lesson with any keyboard, but it will just look like random letters. Not too helpful, in that case.<\\/strong><\\/p>', '<p class=\\\"typinghelp\\\">This lesson is to teach you the Dvorak system of typing.  It is known to allow faster typing because the keys are placed strategically to allow faster finger movement.  QWERTY, on the other hand, was invented to slow a typist down so typewriters would not jam.<\\/p><p class=\\\"typinghelp\\\">This is actually quite a long lesson, and covers all there is to learn of Dvorak, so I hope you get something out of it.<\\/p><p class=\\\"typinghelp\\\"><strong>Be sure to click the \\\"Language & Keyboard\\\" link above and switch to the Dvorak layout if you want to see the proper on-screen keyboard.  Note: You can type this lesson with any keyboard, but it will just look like random letters. Not too helpful, in that case.<\\/strong><\\/p>', 0, '<img src=\\\"\\/tutor\\/images\\/congrats_4.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" align=\\\"right\\\" \\/><p class=\\\"typinghelp\\\">I sure hope you enjoy Dvorak!  You must, if you are seeing this message!<\\/p>', '<img src=\\\"\\/tutor\\/images\\/congrats_4.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" align=\\\"right\\\" \\/><p class=\\\"typinghelp\\\">I sure hope you enjoy Dvorak!  You must, if you are seeing this message!<\\/p>', 'keyboard', NULL);
