(115008, 335, '4-захидал үгс (R - S)', '4-letter words (R - S)', '', '', 'Dear Ross, \\nIt is a real rain. The road is so soft my car \\ncan but roll, stop, and roll on. Are you on the \\nship? If I get as far as the ship, can we sail \\nin such a rain? If we try to sail, the ship is \\nsure to rock or ride on one side. If I get sick, \\nit is up to you to stay by and show us how to \\nsave the ship.', 0, 93, 17, 0, '2014-10-11 13:43:28', 1, NULL),
